MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- layout: swap Quicksand for Space Grotesk (display/body) + JetBrains Mono (labels)
- globals.css: deepen dark bg to #070709, glass cards w/ hairline borders,
  brighten accent to #ff7fae, add .prey-glass/.prey-chip/.prey-label utils,
  scanline + grain + drift + eq + pulse-dot animations, --ac/--acg runtime vars
- BiolinkView: rebuild to match prey card — gradient avatar ring, glass surface,
  mono uppercase labels, refined now-playing (cover + EQ + transport), 3D tilt,
  tasteful scanline/grain; still fully driven by BiolinkConfig
- store: default biolink config to prey values (accent, near-black bg, wider glass card)
