From: rib <you@prey.lol>
Date: Sat, 20 Jun 2026 03:47:19 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] feat(theme): extend prey glass treatment across app
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- brighten all hardcoded muted-pink (#E8769A/#D4638A) to prey accents
  (#ff7fae/#ff6b81/#b58cff) across 12 components
- globals.css: accent selection color, glass saturation on blurred surfaces,
  .prey-lift hover, accent focus ring, reduced-motion guard
- FloatingDock: glass surface + hairline border, accent glow on active item,
  glass hover tooltips
- SplashView: rebuild to prey click-to-enter — gradient-ring avatar,
  Space Grotesk name w/ glitch, mono prompt, pulsing-dot footer
---
 src/app/globals.css                           | 20 +++++
 src/components/ribbon/BiolinkEditor.tsx       |  6 +-
 src/components/ribbon/FloatingDock.tsx        | 13 +--
 src/components/ribbon/MessageInput.tsx        |  2 +-
 src/components/ribbon/TypingIndicator.tsx     |  2 +-
 src/components/ribbon/UserCard.tsx            |  6 +-
 src/components/ribbon/views/DiscoverView.tsx  |  2 +-
 src/components/ribbon/views/FriendsView.tsx   |  4 +-
 src/components/ribbon/views/MobileView.tsx    |  8 +-
 .../ribbon/views/OnboardingView.tsx           | 42 ++++-----
 src/components/ribbon/views/ProfileView.tsx   |  4 +-
 .../ribbon/views/ServerSettingsView.tsx       |  8 +-
 src/components/ribbon/views/SplashView.tsx    | 90 +++++++++++--------
 src/components/ribbon/views/VoiceView.tsx     | 18 ++--
 14 files changed, 132 insertions(+), 93 deletions(-)

diff --git a/src/app/globals.css b/src/app/globals.css
index 8b2b548..bc11244 100755
--- a/src/app/globals.css
+++ b/src/app/globals.css
@@ -439,3 +439,23 @@
   50% { opacity: .5; box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px rgba(255,127,174,0); }
 }
 .prey-pulse-dot { animation: prey-pulse-dot 1.8s infinite; }
+
+/* ═══ prey global polish ═══ */
+/* Soft accent selection highlight */
+::selection { background: rgba(255,127,174,.28); color: #fff; }
+
+/* Any element that opts into blur gets a consistent saturated glass feel */
+[class*="backdrop-blur"] { -webkit-backdrop-filter: saturate(1.15); backdrop-filter: saturate(1.15); }
+
+/* Pill/card hover lift used across views */
+.prey-lift { transition: transform .18s ease, box-shadow .18s ease, border-color .18s ease; }
+.prey-lift:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }
+
+/* Accent ring focus that matches the theme */
+*:focus-visible { outline: 2px solid var(--ac, #ff7fae); outline-offset: 2px; }
+
+/* Respect reduced-motion: kill ambient loops, keep essential transitions */
+@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
+  .animate-prey-drift, .prey-scanlines, .prey-eq-bar, .prey-pulse-dot,
+  .animate-breathe, .animate-twinkle, .animate-drift, .animate-glitch { animation: none !important; }
+}
